US Airways is expanding Caribbean service with five new fun-in-the-sun destinations, including Antigua, Barbados, Cozumel, Grand Bahama Island/Freeport and St. Lucia. By January, US Airways will fly all-jet service to 16 tropical destinations, and a total of 20 Caribbean destinations. If you're looking for fun and sun, travel to the Caribbean on US Airways and let the relaxation begin! Plan your escape from winter now - visit http://www.usairways.com/caribbean for more information and to book a flight. 
