                        US AIRWAYS VACATIONS

US Airways Vacations is pleased to offer Paris land packages to provide a complete vacation experience.

Vacations include accommodations at over 30 hotels for up to 21 nights; hotel taxes and service charges; daily breakfast, Cityrama Sightseeing Tour, "Paris for Less" guidebook, map and discount coupons.  A variety of optional features including sightseeing tours; airport/hotel transfers, rental cars and rail passes are available.

